<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 01:49:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与特朗普家族有联系的比特币矿商连续第二个季度亏损</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</link><description>美国比特币公司是特朗普家族支持的矿商，去年在最大的数字资产从历史高点暴跌之前成立，在其持有的价值下跌后，该公司连续第二个季度亏损。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/itrP8ZGdUt_4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 21:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/trump-family-linked-bitcoin-miner-posts-second-consecutive-quarterly-loss</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 的 Saylor 表示可能转向比特币销售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</link><description>Strategy Inc. 正在削弱其永远不会出售其持有的 670 亿美元比特币的想法。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHeGwBJsXcoQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 05:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/bitcoin-btc-holder-strategy-will-never-say-never-to-selling-reserves</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利首次推出加密货币交易，价格低于竞争对手</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</link><description>摩根士丹利正在其 E*Trade 平台上推出加密货币交易，并讽刺竞争对手：价格更便宜。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2jiKmJEeTcI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 11:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-06/morgan-stanley-debuts-crypto-trading-undercuts-rivals-on-price</guid></item><item><title>拥抱人工智能，否则就会落后：加密货币公司纷纷裁员</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</link><description>加密货币和支付公司一系列与人工智能相关的裁员给分析师和投资者带来了一个好奇的问题：如何评估人工智能部分是否真实？ &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWniLtHgFScg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 19:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/embrace-ai-or-get-left-behind-job-cuts-sweep-through-crypto-firms</guid></item><item><title>策略通过更多炼金术在另一场比特币崩盘中幸存</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</link><description>Michael Saylor 的比特币积累公司 Strategy Inc. 通过一些新的金融工程，在另一场加密货币市场崩溃中幸存下来。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9OlmpClxkrY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 15:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/strategy-survives-another-bitcoin-crash-with-more-alchemy</guid></item><item><title>“忧虑之墙”让散户观望最新的比特币反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</link><description>衡量市场情绪的一个关键指标几周来一直闪烁着看跌信号。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQzk9y1NgXzQ/v6/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-05/-wall-of-worry-has-retail-sitting-out-the-latest-bitcoin-rally</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 以波动的市场和人工智能为由裁员 14%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</link><description>加密货币交易所 Coinbase Global Inc. 将裁员约 14%，理由是需要管理动荡市场的成本和人工智能技术进步。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDpBBVhmfW64/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/coinbase-to-cut-14-of-workforce-citing-volatile-markets-ai</guid></item><item><title>Andreessen Horowitz 筹集 22 亿美元新加密货币基金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/andreessen-horowitz-raises-new-2-2-billion-crypto-fund</link><description>Andreessen Horowitz 筹集了 22 亿美元的加密货币基金，在风险投资行业仍在恢复对该行业的兴趣之际，该基金加倍投资数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTAyEgA5maMo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/andreessen-horowitz-raises-new-2-2-billion-crypto-fund</guid></item><item><title>人工智能最热门的私营公司拥有蓬勃发展的加密货币影子市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</link><description>向散户投资者出售人工智能热潮的一部分的竞赛已经成为主流——封闭式基金、区间基金、特殊用途工具。现在，加密货币平台正在提供与地球上最有价值的私营人工智能公司相关的交易——普通投资者几乎没有其他方式可以参与这些交易。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idJ8est2Gn.M/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 00:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/ai-s-hottest-private-companies-have-booming-crypto-shadow-market</guid></item><item><title>美元主导地位粉碎了拉加德的欧洲加密货币野心</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在货币未来的争夺中，美元拥有巨大的领先优势&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i1mTEn6hIX1g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-05-04/global-crypto-race-why-divided-europe-is-losing-ground</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行的风险投资部门以 10 亿美元的估值支持加密货币公司 GSR</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/stanchart-s-vc-arm-backs-crypto-firm-gsr-at-1-billion-valuation</link><description>随着渣打银行进一步进军数字资产市场，渣打银行全资拥有的风险投资部门 SC Ventures 投资了加密货币交易公司 GSR。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieadhEEYy72U/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 04:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-05/stanchart-s-vc-arm-backs-crypto-firm-gsr-at-1-billion-valuation</guid></item></channel></rss>